## VPS Deployment Steps

```bash
# 1. Clone repo on VPS
git clone <your-repo-url> && cd Crypto-trading-bot

# 2. Create .env from template and fill in API keys
cp docker.env.template .env
nano .env   # Fill in TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, ANTHROPIC_API_KEY, etc.

# 3. Build all images
docker compose build

# 4. Start everything (detached)
docker compose up -d

# 5. Verify all services are running
docker compose ps

# 6. Watch bot logs
docker compose logs -f bot

# 7. Open dashboard
# http://<VPS_IP>:5173
```

## Key Operational Commands

```bash
# Restart a single service
docker compose restart bot

# View logs with timestamps
docker compose logs -f --timestamps bot api

# Stop everything
docker compose down

# Rebuild after code changes
docker compose build && docker compose up -d

# Check which ML data files are being saved
docker compose exec bot ls -la src/ml/data/
```

